<div class="generalitem newsitem"><strong>2013-05-31</strong> (<a href="newsitem.cgi/1369988314" title="Permanent link" rel="bookmark">#</a>) <span class="age">2 months ago</span>
<blockquote>And looking for something else I came across
<a href="http://kmkeen.com/rtl-demod-guide/index.html">rtl_fm guide: the
long lost documentation</a> where the ideas behind it and the command-line
details are better explained. The main idea is to be able to decode FM,
AM, USB and LSB with a light-weight system such as a RaspberryPi.</blockquote>
